msgctxt "188_Tanimura"
msgid "Are you the person who needed some kind of favor?"
msgstr "¿Eres tú? ¿La persona que dijo que tenía algo que hablar conmigo?"

msgctxt "200_Filipino Girl"
msgid "Oh, you're... Tanimura-san, yes? My friend talks about you. She says you're very... kind."
msgstr "Tanimura-san, ¿verdad? Escuché sobre ti por una amiga y vine a conocerte. Es una persona muy buena, eso fue lo que ella dijo."

msgctxt "212_Tanimura"
msgid "Wonder who that is... Anyway, tell me about yourself."
msgstr "¿Y tú quién eres?"

msgctxt "224_Fay"
msgid "I'm Fay, and... I'm a hostess here in Kamurocho."
msgstr "Yo soy Fay. Trabajo en un club de hostesses en Kamurocho."

msgctxt "236_Tanimura"
msgid "Okay... And what is it you want?"
msgstr "Entonces, ¿cuál es el problema?"

msgctxt "248_Fay"
msgid "I want you to... be my boyfriend!"
msgstr "¡Por favor! ¡¡Sé mi novio!!"

msgctxt "260_Fay"
msgid "I'll do anything for you! Anything! So please, be my boyfriend!"
msgstr "¡Puedo hacer cualquier cosa! ¡¡Por favor, Sea mi novio!!"

msgctxt "272_Tanimura"
msgid "Whoa, slow down there! What's all this boyfriend stuff about? You don't even know me."
msgstr "¡¡Eh...!! ¿Qué estás diciendo de repente?\n"
"\n"
"Primero, explícame la razón."

msgctxt "284_Fay"
msgid "Does that mean... you won't be my boyfriend?"
msgstr "Eh, um... ¿No seras mi novio?"

msgctxt "296_Tanimura"
msgid "I don't know why you thought I would. Is there some kind of reason you're looking for a boyfriend so bad?"
msgstr "No sé por qué pensaste que lo haría. ¿Hay alguna razón por la que busques un novio con tanta urgencia?"

msgctxt "308_Fay"
msgid "Well, if... If you were my boyfriend, I thought maybe you could... save me."
msgstr "Eh... esto... Por favor, sea en mi novio, necesito tu ayuda."

msgctxt "320_Tanimura"
msgid "Save you? From what? Is somebody after you?"
msgstr "¿Salvarte? ¿De qué? ¿Hay alguien que te persigue?"

msgctxt "332_Fay"
msgid "There... was a man I was dating... who did some terrible\\r\n"
"things. Things that landed him in prison."
msgstr "Sí... había un hombre con el que salía. Ese hombre...\\r\n"
"hizo cosas malas y terminó en prisión."

msgctxt "344_Fay"
msgid "But now he's back in Kamurocho, and the first thing he did was find me."
msgstr "Pero ese hombre... regresó a Kamurocho y vino a buscarme..."

msgctxt "356_Fay"
msgid "He took all my money... which I need to send back home to the Philippines. I thought I'd never see him again, but he forced his way back into my life..."
msgstr "Me robó mi dinero. El dinero que envío a Filipinas... Quiero separarme de ese hombre."

msgctxt "368_Fay"
msgid "That's why I need your help, Tanimura-san. Please be my new boyfriend－even if it's just for today－and make my old one go away."
msgstr "Así que, Tanimura-san... sé en mi novio y ahuyenta a ese tipo."

msgctxt "380_Tanimura"
msgid "Let me get this straight: you're trying to ditch your loser\\r\n"
"of an ex, so you want me to pretend to be your man just so\\r\n"
"he'll get the message?"
msgstr "Entiendo... Quieres terminar con tu novio mantenido,\\r\n"
"así que deseas que yo finja ser tu novio y hable de\\r\n"
"la ruptura, ¿verdad?"

msgctxt "392_Fay"
msgid "Yes. I'd like you to talk to him and make him leave me alone."
msgstr "Así es. Quiero que le hables de la ruptura."

msgctxt "404_Fay"
msgid "Please, just this once! Won't you be my boyfriend?"
msgstr "Tanimura-san, ¡por favor! ¡¡Sea en mi novio!!"

msgctxt "416_Tanimura"
msgid "Fine, I'll do it. Though I'm not quite sure how you want this to work."
msgstr "Está bien, seré tu novio. Entonces... ¿qué se supone que debemos hacer?"

msgctxt "428_Fay"
msgid "Thank you! You have no idea how much this means to me...\\r\n"
"As for how to go about this..."
msgstr "¡Gracias! ¡¡Muchas gracias, Tanimura-san!!\\r\n"
"Entonces..."

msgctxt "440_Fay"
msgid "First, I need to call my ex-boyfriend and invite him to Shellac. You and I will be waiting there."
msgstr "Llamaré al hombre... así que, ven a \"Shellac\". Estaré esperando."

msgctxt "452_Tanimura"
msgid "Shellac... That's in the Champion District. Okay, got it."
msgstr "El \"Shellac\" en el Distrito Champion, ¿verdad? Entendido.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"

msgctxt "464_Fay"
msgid "Ah, that's such a relief. I'll meet you there, okay? Please don't forget to show up."
msgstr "Entonces, iré primero. ¡Asegúrate de venir, Tanimura-san!"

msgctxt "524_Tanimura"
msgid "Well, guess I'd better get on over to Shellac. This should be fun."
msgstr "Bueno... Entonces, yo también me dirigiré a \"Shellac\"."

msgctxt "548_Tanimura"
msgid "Yeah, you need to ask somebody else. Breaking up with bad\\r\n"
"boyfriends is not what I signed up for."
msgstr "Lo siento, pide ayuda a otra persona. Hablar de rupturas no\\r\n"
"es parte del trabajo de la policía."

msgctxt "560_Fay"
msgid "But... you're the only person I can ask."
msgstr "No hay nadie más a quien pueda pedir ayuda que no sea Tanimura-san..."

msgctxt "572_Fay"
msgid "Whenever there's a problem to be solved, people mention your\\r\n"
"name all the time... I thought your duty was to help people."
msgstr "Me dijeron que usted Tanimura-san, solo usted podría ayudarme...\\r"

msgctxt "584_Tanimura"
msgid "I'm flattered, but I'm not the guy for the job. But you know\\r\n"
"who might be? Take a good look over there."
msgstr "Si solo necesitas a alguien que haga el papel de novio, no necesariamente\\r\n"
"tengo que ser yo. ¿Qué tal Zhao-san el de allí?"

msgctxt "596_Zhao"
msgid "Hm? You guys need something?"
msgstr "¿Mmm...?\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"

msgctxt "608_Fay"
msgid "You mean... him? Will... anyone really believe we're dating?"
msgstr "Es imposible... el no puede ser a mi novio."

msgctxt "620_Tanimura"
msgid "...Yeah, maybe not."
msgstr "Ya veo..."

msgctxt "632_Fay"
msgid "See? You're my only hope, Tanimura-san... All I can do now is wait for you to change your mind."
msgstr "No hay nadie más que Tanimura-san. Estare esperando... Por favor, ayúdeme."

msgctxt "644_Tanimura"
msgid "I'll at least mull it over in my head. For now, I've got actual police work to do. Kinda."
msgstr "Si me animo. Bueno, también tengo trabajo que hacer."

msgctxt "656_Fay"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "716_Fay"
msgid "Save me, Tanimura-san... Please be my boyfriend, just for today."
msgstr "Tanimura-san, sea en mi novio y ayúdeme..."

msgctxt "728_Tanimura"
msgid "Fine, I'll do it. Though I'm not quite sure how you want this to work."
msgstr "Está bien, seré tu novio. Entonces... ¿qué se supone que debemos hacer?"

msgctxt "740_Fay"
msgid "Thank you! You have no idea how much this means to me...\\r\n"
"As for how to go about this..."
msgstr "¡Gracias! ¡¡Muchas gracias, Tanimura-san!!\\r\n"
"Entonces..."

msgctxt "752_Fay"
msgid "First, I need to call my ex-boyfriend and invite him to Shellac. You and I will be waiting there."
msgstr "Llamaré al hombre... así que, ven a \"Shellac\". Estaré esperando."

msgctxt "764_Tanimura"
msgid "Shellac... That's in the Champion District. Okay, got it."
msgstr "El \"Shellac\" en el Distrito Champion, ¿verdad? Entendido.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"

msgctxt "776_Fay"
msgid "Ah, that's such a relief. I'll meet you there, okay? Please don't forget to show up."
msgstr "Entonces, iré primero. ¡Asegúrate de venir, Tanimura-san!"

msgctxt "836_Tanimura"
msgid "Well, guess I'd better get on over to Shellac. This should be fun."
msgstr "Bueno... Entonces, yo también me dirigiré a \"Shellac\"."

msgctxt "860_Tanimura"
msgid "Maybe when I have time. For now, I suggest you ask someone else."
msgstr "Está bien, seré tu novio. Entonces... ¿qué se supone que debemos hacer?"

msgctxt "872_Fay"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "896_Tanimura"
msgid "Yeah, ask somebody else."
msgstr "Lo siento, por favor, pida ayuda a otra persona."

msgctxt "908_Tanimura"
msgid "Fine, I'll do it."
msgstr "Entendido, seré tu novio."

msgctxt "920_Tanimura"
msgid "Fine, I'll do it."
msgstr "Entendido, seré tu novio."

msgctxt "932_Tanimura"
msgid "Sorry, ask someone else."
msgstr "Lo siento, pregúntale a otro."

